            <td><div class="price-labor">$140–$280</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ module or gear if needed</div></td>
            <td>Ice maker module gears, auger motor (French door models), ice bin positioning. Ice jam clearing often resolves noise.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr >
